<link rel="stylesheet" media="all" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220123234700cs_/https://boards.cdn.greenhouse.io/assets/responsive-95ad71d0f9cbcb13adb28ed74687b15c00a64bb1c4a6ab47ab9072493777804c.css"/>
  
  
    <meta property="og:title" content="Beauty Pie"></meta>
    <meta property="og:description" content="We’re the first-ever buyer’s club for beauty product lovers. We’re a team of beauty-product obsessives who have worked in the cosmetics and wellness industries for eons. And we’ve figured out that the way the old beauty industry works, is a bit of a rip-off. At BEAUTY PIE, our mission is to make our customer feel like a kid in a candy store. To bring them the fairy tale. To deliver the absolute best in beauty nonstop, at prices so amazing, even a splurge is a steal.  
Now, unlike a lot of start-ups, our business model is solid. And the best part? We save our customers a bundle. In fact, the products (and the prices) we deliver are so good, we believe we’re about to take over the premium beauty business. How? By getting our members a way bigger piece of the BEAUTY PIE.
As part of our team? You’ll learn a lot. (We’re all learning a lot.) You’ll be multi-tasking, you’ll make some great decisions and some bad ones. You’ll have highs and lows. It won’t be easy (because that would be boring). But you’ll be moving fast, identifying and solving problems, iterating and evolving, and you’ll bring your best to the game. In fact, it’s not very often you get an opportunity like this - to help grow a great brand, for a rocketship of a business that will scale in size and go global. One that thrills its customers. And delivers happiness. We'll be asking for your input, experience, teamwork, ideas, and camaraderie, while we navigate the unknown, the mysterious and the upside together! 
Our Values. Our culture is our DNA. It defines who we are, how we operate and how we hire based on our values:

Bring Your ‘A’ Game - take ownership &amp;amp; accountability, make shit happen, grow, support, evolve, invent, be open minded 
Be Intelligently Rebellious - challenge the status quo, push boundaries, embrace change and think big
Be Customer Obsessed - listen &amp;amp; learn, take ownership, act fast, be humble &amp;amp; empathetic, build &amp;amp; keep trust, be grateful for feedback
It’s All For One (&amp;amp; One For All) - take advantage of collective intelligence, act with integrity, support &amp;amp; challenge, embrace individuality, do right by our company, our members, our colleagues &amp;amp; our environment
"></meta>
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://web.archive.org/web/20220123234700/https://boards.eu.greenhouse.io/beautypie"></meta>
